snippet.title: My Beauty Salon | Baby John Songs And Little Angel Nursery Rhymes
snippet.description:
Welcome to Jill’s Beauty Salon! She can style your hair or give you a make up! First Jack shows up, then Baby John! Even Mommy and Daddy are involved! Watch as the family visits her shop and get her services in this new video by Little Angel. #littleangel #littleangelnurseryrhymes #babyjohnsongs 

(🔔) Subscribe to Little Angel for New Videos ►► http://bit.ly/Subscribe_to_LittleAngel

Song Lyrics

Come, come along
This is my salon
Yeah!
Hair-cuts and dress-up!
So much fun fun fun!

Come sit here
Don’t fear!

Cause…

Here we go, here we go
This is so much fun!
Here we go, here we go
Now we’re almost done!

Here we go, here we go
This is so much fun!
Here we go, here we go
And now we’re done!

Come, come along
This is my salon
Yeah!
Animals? I paint them all!
So much fun fun fun!

Come sit here
Don’t fear!

Cause…

Here we go, here we go
This is so much fun!
Here we go, here we go
Now we’re almost done!

Here we go, here we go
This is so much fun!
Here we go, here we go
And now we’re done!

Come, come along
This is my salon
Yeah!
Face masks to relax
So much fun fun fun!

Come sit here
Don’t fear!

Cause…

Here we go, here we go
This is so much fun!
Here we go, here we go
Now we’re almost done!

Here we go, here we go
This is so much fun!
Here we go, here we go
And now we’re done!

Come, come along
This is my salon
Yeah!
It’s time for girl time!
So much fun fun fun!

Come sit here
Don’t fear!

Cause…

Here we go, here we go
This is so much fun!
Here we go, here we go
Now we’re almost done!

Here we go, here we go
This is so much fun!
Here we go, here we go
And now we’re done!
